articles.author: DeFi Surfer
articles.description:
Absolutely no way this is sustainable. https://twitter.com/charliebilello/status/1650885984135921664

Charlie Bilello: 3 years ago: 30-yr mortgage rate was 2.97% & average new home price in the US was $360k.
Today: 30-yr mortgage rate is 6.39% & average new home price is $562k.
Result: $40k increase in down payment (assuming 20% down) & 132% increase in monthly payment (from $1,209 to $2,809).
articles.title: Absolutely no way this is sustainable. https://twitter.com/charliebilello/status/1650885984135921664
